iations of, and decisions on, norms and ideals of citizenship, freedom, equality, property, democracy, gender, and family life – negotiations and decisions that come with legacies that shape the present.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aArchitektur. 0aBerlin. 0aCity planningxHistoryy20th centuryzAustriazVienna. 0aCity planningxHistoryy20th centuryzGermanyzBerlin. 0aHousing policyxHistoryy20th centuryzAustriazVienna. 0aHousing policyxHistoryy20th centuryzGermanyzBerlin. 0aNachkriegszeit. 0aPublic housingxHistoryy20th centuryzAustriazVienna. 0aPublic housingxHistoryy20th centuryzGermanyzBerlin. 0aWien. 0aWohnungsbau. 4aArt and Material Culture. 4aSocial and Political Sciences. 4aSociology and Social History. 4aUrban Cultures. 7aARCHITECTURE / History / Modern (late 19th Century to 1945).2bisacsh  aUrban and social history, political ideologies, public housing, the return of the housing question.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023z978311102374808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2023z9783111318097oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2023 Englishz978311131903208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048552702?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789048552702423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9789048552702/original  a978-3-11-102374-8  Amsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  a978-3-11-131903-2  EBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architec